{"tid":902109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽抽光70多個扭蛋不中大獎　控訴美樂士多呃人：真心嬲","createTime":"2018-11-14T14:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T01:30:40.000Z","uid":202698,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e93055c2450102a496eb912247c2c45be34c554a","tid":902109,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"港媽抽光70多個扭蛋不中大獎　控訴美樂士多呃人：真心嬲<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2207423/meilok_thumb_20181113_ch_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2207423%2Fmeilok_thumb_20181113_ch_v2_1024.jpg&h=e361af93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港一些士多店會在扭蛋內放入紙條，可換取不同的小禮物。然而荃灣愉景新城內一間名為「美樂士多」的商店，卻出現扭蛋「騙局」。<span style=\"color: red;\">一名港媽帶女兒扭蛋，花了數百元扭足70多次，把全機扭蛋扭清，仍未抽中女兒最想要的大鈴鐺。</span>事主在facebook發文公開事件，涉事「美樂士多」亦在facebook發文道歉，稱會暫停相關扭蛋機遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">＂如果不是我扭光所有波，你們(商店)就繼續呃人了！＂</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n事主在facebook發文指，日前帶女兒到商店扭鈴鐺，20元可扭3次，女兒想扭到大的鈴鐺，Jennifer見裡面的扭蛋不多，就讓女兒扭，不料扭了300元仍只得小鈴鐺。當時機內只剩下10個扭蛋，店員說會扭到大鈴鐺，於是她再花100元讓女兒繼續扭，最終扭光機內70多隻扭蛋。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">＂到最後有點生氣扭光你的波，不料仍然沒有！原來都是「呃人」的，細的就有得扭，大的被扭出來後，就沒有再重新放回去被人抽，真心嬲！＂</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n事主生氣地質問店員是否騙人，又謂「做生意不是這樣做」。從她拍攝的照片可見，掛著禮物鈴鐺的牌，只剩8個大鈴鐺，其餘都已被她抽中。她認為，如果不是她把全部扭蛋抽光，店舖會繼續騙人，決定公開事件，令其他人不會受騙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2207423/01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2207423%2F01_1024.jpg&h=cdfa90f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商店發文道歉<br />\n<br />\n美樂士多隨後在facebook公開道歉，表示事件令家長失望，他們也對自己感到失望，又指以往從未想過會發生這種事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當向店同事了解之後，發覺是同事扣起了部分號碼紙，沒有全部放入機內。美樂士多責無旁貸，絕對是我們的過失！管理不善！</span><br />\n<br />\n美樂士多向客人致歉，又指會先暫停扭蛋機遊戲，直至找到不會出錯的方式。不過，網民卻認為店舖把責任推給員工，亦另有苦主指自己抽了10多個都是小鈴鐺，不會再光顧等。"},{"pid":"54f269804416b16853f3a83d320ad22566476955","tid":902109,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"間間都係<br />\n有價值會有人散買直接拿走"},{"pid":"5d4d51be4175884d8c221f9953fe178c2481b246","tid":902109,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"諗起達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136e249a411a0b76d1110726a13d719103c5392d","tid":902109,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4d1198c364a8f45f303e5cbd6ab6413199d100","tid":902109,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d4d51be4175884d8c221f9953fe178c2481b246","tid":902109,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"諗起達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"阿婆 你出術喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b88f46ef02c280506dc2b6faca9b60f960c33a","tid":902109,"uid":10757,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"個港媽又幾又童心 洗成幾舊水 扭哂終於知原來冇大獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574327e88e18c795006cc366227a4d08d99598d6","tid":902109,"uid":121409,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"b5b88f46ef02c280506dc2b6faca9b60f960c33a","tid":90210